com.adobe.aem.commons.assetshare.util

Class ComponentModelVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.sling.api.resource.AbstractResourceVisitor
      • com.adobe.aem.commons.assetshare.util.ResourceTypeVisitor
        • com.adobe.aem.commons.assetshare.util.ComponentModelVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The Model type to collect.

    public final class ComponentModelVisitor<T>
extends ResourceTypeVisitor
    Utility visitor that walks a Page and collects the models for resources matching at least one of the provided resource Types. This visitor only visits resources with a sling:resourceType.

    • Method Detail

      • getModels

        public final Collection<T> getModels()
        Note that getModels() may return a SUBSET of getResources(). If a resource matches the resource type check but cannot be turned into a model, the resources will be in getResources() but not in getModels().
        Returns:
        a list of Models representing the visited resources (assuming they match the resourceTypes and can be made into the clazz model type.
